ttle experimentation with it.  However, I can't seem to get it to work durring duels to test it (Might be extremely unlucky, but I get the feeling it doesn't work for duels).  I'd like to hear from anyone who's used it as to how often it works.  Otherwise it's just wasting 5pp I can use towards peridots.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Damastes Argent<br>
51 Vicar of Innoruuk<br>
Iron Throne <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/bbrellserilis.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=elmeric>Elmeric</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Fellow of Underfoot</span><br>   <font color=#CC9900>(6/30/00 2:26:00 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Death Pact</span><hr size=1> death pact is the spell that offers a saving throw versus death when you die and if you pass you get healed to 50% hp right? and it has a reagent-pearl. im not sure on the names of cleric spells, but if this is the one im talking about, then it rocks.<br>
<br>
semele cast it on me a few times and it saved my ass once. im pretty sure she could offer you alot more info on the spell cause she asked for feedback on the people she cast it on <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> . i can see it not working in duels, because in the name of 'balance' we must restrict the caster classes full abilities. <br>
<br>
/rude ice comet not doing 1120 damage in a duel<br>
<br>
Elmeric <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/udamastes.showPublicProfile>Damastes</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Fellow of Underfoot</span><br>   <font color=#CC9900>(6/30/00 3:28:14 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Death Pact</span><hr size=1> Aye, that be the one I'm talking about.  As a side note though, the only thing it seemed to do in duels was cancel the duel and make you lose exp. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :/ --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/ohwell.gif ALT=":/"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Don't know if it's bugged or what.  Not fun when you realize you lost exp in 51 either.  Just a warning to those that try it out in a duel.<br>
<br>
<br>
Damastes <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/ulanaritalonheart.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lanari Talonheart</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>   <font color=#CC9900>(7/13/00 10:55:02 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Death Pact</span><hr size=1> I had a very nice warrior volunteer to try it out for me at the zone of sebilis, and he didn't mind dying to see if it would work.  Very nice of him.  Needless to say it actually worked<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Find a willing guinee pig.<br>
<br>
----------<br>
Lanari <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/bbrellserilis.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=khalen>Khalen</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>   <font color=#CC9900>(7/21/00 11:07:30 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Death Pact</span><hr size=1> Actually I find Death Pact almost a waste of the reg. It will only heal a greater heal close to the time of death. This is hardly the worth of 5-6 pp reg.<br>
<br>
My thoughts are that death pact was meant to be a Cleric Buff for the new unswerving hammer spell. Once cast on your pet he will no longer suicide but become a regular pet very similar to the Enchanter Pet. Pet will last till killed or untill DP spell wears off 1 hr later. <p>Khalen O'Lan<br>
55th Templar Skyre Draneth<br>
Brell Server<br>
"The Promise of Life"
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/uhoolihan4077.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hoolihan4077</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>   <font color=#CC9900>(7/29/00 12:35:00 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Death Pact</span><hr size=1> It's a nice spell indeed and I have no doubt it will work. I have just not seen it do so yet and have cast it on numerous group members many times. I guess they just don't die enough! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  I'm not using it anymore except on high risk group members such as pullers and chanters. Is this spell worth all it's cracked up to be really?<br>
<br>
Regards Hoolihan <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/ukraghack.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kraghack</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>   <font color=#CC9900>(7/29/00 1:53:51 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Death Pact</span><hr size=1> <br>
